{"tid":1066741,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 擋箭救人一命，澳洲男子僅輕傷，有如電影情節！","createTime":"2019-03-18T05:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T07:55:46.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"653c09f2c8abd48c82d85e6b90aee4f9d7e92ed3","tid":1066741,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/03/17/iphonesavelife-2/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F03%2F17%2Fiphonesavelife-2%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=26ae4a44\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/03/17/iphonesavelife-2/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n事件發生在澳洲新南威爾斯州裡面的一條村落，這條村落還遺留了自由開放買賣大麻的傳統。在今個月 13 日的一個早上，一名 43 歲的男性返回家中剛從汽車步出，即發現一名曾見過面的男子在家門前埋伏。<br />\n<br />\n事主認識該名埋伏者，但他今次卻穿武裝手上並拿著弓矢。事主馬上拿起手機這名不速之客拍下，而埋伏者就在此時向事主發箭攻擊。飛箭直向事主的臉飛去，幸好此時手機成為了他的盾牌，僅下巴受到輕傷。當時手機貼有保護貼。該名埋伏者最後被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F02.jpg&h=f33d42d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f577c3bceaa8aa930def69e1967dbecb575f8c5f","tid":1066741,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:36:57.000Z","msg":"以往亦曾發生過 iPhone 擋子彈的事件，如今智能手機再次以「物理」救人，可說是另一個奇跡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kT85Je4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkT85Je4.png&h=f706fc44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nswpolice/status/1105788359241195521\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnswpolice%2Fstatus%2F1105788359241195521&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=0441690d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnswpolice%2Fstatus%2F1105788359241195521&h=ece07c8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nswpolice/status/1105788359241195521</a>"},{"pid":"98d57d4182568e30e8bc940dbc71c4333b5b7ee6","tid":1066741,"uid":151324,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:37:38.000Z","msg":"android狗去晒邊"},{"pid":"9d5366c17deac056ffc4e6847b5841d8b97ab1fa","tid":1066741,"uid":156376,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"Nokia的話應該支箭斷左"},{"pid":"3c315870982bef023376aa6dca08e452063a7f51","tid":1066741,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:40:24.000Z","msg":"下次拎macbook擋麻，已碼擋嘅面積更大"},{"pid":"dfade602cf34408dd6b515ac1117f5f335abec01","tid":1066741,"uid":214011,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"Apple 可以加返落去<br />\n敢問 iPhone 有多本事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone/features/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fiphone%2Ffeatures%2F&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=2ad6027d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.apple.com/hk/iphone/features/</a>"},{"pid":"6f55a7d69814bf490098f571da94a29fdae399c8","tid":1066741,"uid":26333,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9d5366c17deac056ffc4e6847b5841d8b97ab1fa","tid":1066741,"uid":156376,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"Nokia的話應該支箭斷左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"APPEL真係水皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5baab613052d880be9afc79dededb1433f8bea03","tid":1066741,"uid":194130,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9d5366c17deac056ffc4e6847b5841d8b97ab1fa","tid":1066741,"uid":156376,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"Nokia的話應該支箭斷左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:39:01.000Z","msg":"斷就應該唔會既<br />\n應該係彈開左支箭拎返出黎仲可以打電話<br />\n邊似Apple咁比人射穿<img src=\"/